http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/kozhikode/Footwear-exhibition-hopes-to-raise-up-to-Rs.-10-crore/article13996325.ece

Various footwear products from 150 manufacturers will be on display from January 15 to 17 on Marine Ground here, under the Brand Kerala Footwear Expo.Organised by Footwear Manufacturers Association of Kerala, the expo will also provide a platform for the local brands in the State.Association president C.P. Aboobacker said on Monday that dealers from States such as Karnataka, Tamil Nadu and Maharashtra, those from the United Arab Emirates and Saudi Arabia would also participate.“We expect purchases to range from Rs.5 lakh to Rs.10 crore,” he said. The association would give prizes for high value purchases.